Margin - space between block and other blocks
    Border - box surrounding padding and content
        Padding - space between content and border
            Content

Margin
    margin size in px

        Border
            size, style, color;
            example: 3px, solid, black

            Padding
                Padding size in px

                    Content
                        height;
                        width;



All of these can also be applied only to top, bottom, left, right, etc by specificying (example: border-bottom: 10px;)
